---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title={'How It Works — Goldfin Group'} description={'One partner coordinating your entire financial picture: the 15-minute call, your number, the team built and led, and twice-yearly Proactive Planning Sessions.'} path={'/how-it-works'}>
<div class="pagehead">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">How it works</p>
    <h1>One quarterback. <em>Every dot connected.</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">A team with no leader is just highly skilled individuals running around the field. If they score, it's by chance. Here's what our coordination actually looks like.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="num-steps">
      <div class="step"><div class="n">01</div><div><h3>The 15-minute call</h3><p>No pitch. We talk about where you are: thinking about selling, under LOI, or staring at the wire. You leave with the questions you should be asking, whether or not we ever work together.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="n">02</div><div><h3>Your number, reverse-engineered</h3><p>Not the number you want. The number you need: after taxes, fees, family obligations, giving, and what your month-to-month life actually costs. Every negotiation gets easier once you know it.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="n">03</div><div><h3>The team, built and led</h3><p>Tax strategists, M&A advisors, attorneys, bankers: we make the introductions, set the agenda, and call the plays so their work compounds instead of colliding.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="n">04</div><div><h3>The Proactive Planning Session, twice a year</h3><p>April and November. We review the tape, update the buckets, revisit the mandate, and get ahead of the next tax year instead of reacting to the last one.</p></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-row" style="margin-top:50px">
      <a class="btn btn-gold" href="/book">Book a 15-minute call</a>
      <span class="quiet">Conversations get serious around $1M+ in annual profit.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
